                <note rend="inline" type="source">763.72/3314½</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-02-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 7, 1917</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Saw the Cuban Minister and advised him that it would be unwise for Cuba to break
                    off diplomatic relations with Germany. He said that he would so advise his
                    Govt</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
